<br>
Disease damage is rarely resisted by mobs and will make for a 12/21 weapon most of the time for you.  Sweet deal for ya.<br>
<br>
The Goronga club is nice for keeping the skill up and doing damage but agro is going to be better with the 10/21 (mostly 12/21) than the 12/23.<br>
