<br>
The ONLY bonus damage type that is added to the base damage is BANE damage. Disease damage is a damage bonus added at the end of the hit calculation (just like the inherent damage bonus that each melees gets with their main hand.)<br>
<br>
SO, that said, the fungus is still your best mainhand weapon. 10/21 is your fastest weapon (and remember you want your fastest weapon in mainhand so that the damage bonus gets applied as often as possible).<br>
<br>
For the offhand, it's gonna depend if you're hasted or not. If you're hasted, take the BBoT cause you'll probably be able to proc a lot and hold aggro that way. However, if you're not hasted, you're not gonna proc very often with a 22 delay weapon, so go for the superior damage of the 12/23 (pretty nice ratio actually).<br>
<br>
When xping, always take the 12/23 as the proc off the 9/22 will not make up for the extra damage.<br>
<br>
